Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
RUClinic.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Appointment>
Direct Known Subclasses:
Imaging
public class Appointment extends Object implements Comparable<Appointment>
The Appointment class is used to create appointments in the clinic that contain the date and time of the appointment, the name of the patient and the name of the provider that is being seen. This class serves as the backbone of the project, since Appointment objects are the main focus.
